### Hadith 2:608

*Narrated Ibn 'Umar :*

Allah's Apostle used to go (for Hajj) via Ash-Shajara way and return via
Muarras way; and no doubt, whenever Allah's Apostle went to Mecca, he
used to offer the prayer in the Mosque of Ash-Shajara; and on his
return, he used to offer the prayer at Dhul-Hulaifa in the middle of the
valley, and pass the night there till morning.

